                  </div>
                  <span class=""></span>
                    <p class="mb-5">Get down to business with Tomahawk King‘s premium grills. Meat lovers will find themselves at home with the joint’s mouthwatering cuts, from Premium Australian Ribeye Steak to the juicy and succulent Tomalamb.<br><br>The Mixed Platter includes flavourful mid-wings, prawn gyoza, potato wedges, calamari, and Farci crab, perfect for four to six people. For those craving something local, Chargrilled Chicken and Beef Satay are also available. Tomahawk King’s selection of delicious meats makes it one of the best casual restaurants in Singapore to unwind and loosen up after a long day.<br><br>Where: 324F Changi Road, Singapore, 419799</p>

                    <h3 class>8. Yun Nans</h3>
